283 class FrostwingVrykulSearcher
284 {
285 public:
286  FrostwingVrykulSearcher(Creature const* source, float range) : _source(source), _range(range) {}
287 
288  bool operator()(Unit* unit)
289  {
290  if (!unit->IsAlive())
291  return false;
292 
293  switch (unit->GetEntry())
294  {
295  case NPC_YMIRJAR_BATTLE_MAIDEN:
296  case NPC_YMIRJAR_DEATHBRINGER:
297  case NPC_YMIRJAR_FROSTBINDER:
298  case NPC_YMIRJAR_HUNTRESS:
299  case NPC_YMIRJAR_WARLORD:
300  break;
301  default:
302  return false;
303  }
304 
305  if (!unit->IsWithinDist(_source, _range, false))
306  return false;
307 
308  return true;
309  }
310 
311 private:
312  Creature const* _source;
313  float _range;
314 };
315 
316 class FrostwingGauntletRespawner
317 {
318 public:
319  void operator()(Creature* creature)
320  {
321  switch (creature->GetOriginalEntry())
322  {
323  case NPC_YMIRJAR_BATTLE_MAIDEN:
324  case NPC_YMIRJAR_DEATHBRINGER:
325  case NPC_YMIRJAR_FROSTBINDER:
326  case NPC_YMIRJAR_HUNTRESS:
327  case NPC_YMIRJAR_WARLORD:
328  break;
329  case NPC_CROK_SCOURGEBANE:
330  case NPC_CAPTAIN_ARNATH:
331  case NPC_CAPTAIN_BRANDON:
332  case NPC_CAPTAIN_GRONDEL:
333  case NPC_CAPTAIN_RUPERT:
334  creature->AI()->DoAction(ACTION_RESET_EVENT);
335  break;
336  case NPC_SISTER_SVALNA: // she never dies or the event is over
337  creature->AI()->DoAction(ACTION_RESET_EVENT);
338  creature->AI()->EnterEvadeMode();
339  creature->AI()->Reset();
340  return;
341  default:
342  return;
343  }
344 
345  if (CreatureData const* data = creature->GetCreatureData())
346  creature->SetPosition(data->posX, data->posY, data->posZ, data->orientation);
347  creature->DespawnOrUnsummon();
348 
349  creature->SetRespawnTime(5);
350  }
351 };

389  // IMPORTANT NOTE: This is triggered from per-GUID scripts
390  // of The Damned SAI
391  void SetData(uint32 type, uint32 data) override
392  {
393  if (type == DATA_DAMNED_KILLS && data == 1)
394  {
395  if (++_damnedKills == 2)
396  {
397  if (Creature* theLichKing = me->FindNearestCreature(NPC_THE_LICH_KING_LH, 150.0f))
398  {
399  if (Creature* bolvarFordragon = me->FindNearestCreature(NPC_HIGHLORD_BOLVAR_FORDRAGON_LH, 150.0f))
400  {
401  if (Creature* factionNPC = me->FindNearestCreature(_instance->GetData(DATA_TEAMID_IN_INSTANCE) == TEAM_HORDE ? NPC_HIGH_OVERLORD_SAURFANG_DUMMY : NPC_MURADIN_BRONZEBEARD_DUMMY, 50.0f))
402  {
403  me->setActive(true);
404  _theLichKing = theLichKing->GetGUID();
405  theLichKing->setActive(true);
406  _bolvarFordragon = bolvarFordragon->GetGUID();
407  bolvarFordragon->setActive(true);
408  _factionNPC = factionNPC->GetGUID();
409  factionNPC->setActive(true);
410  }
411  }
412  }
413 
414  if (!_bolvarFordragon || !_theLichKing || !_factionNPC)
415  return;
416 
417  Talk(SAY_TIRION_INTRO_1);
418  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_2, 4000);
419  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_3, 14000);
420  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_4, 18000);
421  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_5, 31000);
422  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_LK_INTRO_1, 35000);
423  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_6, 49000);
424  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_LK_INTRO_2, 58000);
425  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_LK_INTRO_3, 74000);
426  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_LK_INTRO_4, 86000); // sound last 21 seconds (five more)
427  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_BOLVAR_INTRO_1, 107000);
428  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_LK_INTRO_5, 113000);
429 
430  if (_instance->GetData(DATA_TEAMID_IN_INSTANCE) == TEAM_HORDE)
431  {
432  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SAURFANG_INTRO_1, 125000);
433  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_H_7, 134000);
434  _events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SAURFANG_INTRO_2, 144000);

453  void UpdateAI(uint32 diff) override
454  {
455  if (_damnedKills != 2)
456  return;
457 
458  _events.Update(diff);
459 
460  while (uint32 eventId = _events.ExecuteEvent())
461  {
462  switch (eventId)
463  {
464  case EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_2:
465  me->HandleEmoteCommand(EMOTE_ONESHOT_EXCLAMATION);
466  break;
467  case EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_3:
468  Talk(SAY_TIRION_INTRO_2);
469  break;
470  case EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_4:
471  me->HandleEmoteCommand(EMOTE_ONESHOT_EXCLAMATION);
472  break;
473  case EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_5:
474  Talk(SAY_TIRION_INTRO_3);
475  break;
476  case EVENT_LK_INTRO_1:
477  me->HandleEmoteCommand(EMOTE_ONESHOT_POINT_NO_SHEATHE);
478  if (Creature* theLichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _theLichKing))
479  theLichKing->AI()->Talk(SAY_LK_INTRO_1);
480  break;
481  case EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_6:
482  Talk(SAY_TIRION_INTRO_4);
483  break;
484  case EVENT_LK_INTRO_2:
485  if (Creature* theLichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _theLichKing))
486  theLichKing->AI()->Talk(SAY_LK_INTRO_2);
487  break;
488  case EVENT_LK_INTRO_3:
489  if (Creature* theLichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _theLichKing))
490  theLichKing->AI()->Talk(SAY_LK_INTRO_3);
491  break;
492  case EVENT_LK_INTRO_4:
493  if (Creature* theLichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _theLichKing))
494  theLichKing->AI()->Talk(SAY_LK_INTRO_4);
495  break;
496  case EVENT_BOLVAR_INTRO_1:
497  if (Creature* bolvarFordragon = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _bolvarFordragon))
498  {
499  bolvarFordragon->AI()->Talk(SAY_BOLVAR_INTRO_1);
500  bolvarFordragon->setActive(false);
501  }
502  break;
503  case EVENT_LK_INTRO_5:
504  if (Creature* theLichKing = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _theLichKing))
505  {
506  theLichKing->AI()->Talk(SAY_LK_INTRO_5);
507  theLichKing->setActive(false);
508  }
509  break;
510  case EVENT_SAURFANG_INTRO_1:
511  if (Creature* saurfang = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _factionNPC))
512  saurfang->AI()->Talk(SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_1);
513  break;
514  case EVENT_TIRION_INTRO_H_7:
515  Talk(SAY_TIRION_INTRO_H_5);
516  break;
517  case EVENT_SAURFANG_INTRO_2:
518  if (Creature* saurfang = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _factionNPC))
519  saurfang->AI()->Talk(SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_2);
520  break;
521  case EVENT_SAURFANG_INTRO_3:
522  if (Creature* saurfang = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _factionNPC))
523  saurfang->AI()->Talk(SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_3);
524  break;
525  case EVENT_SAURFANG_INTRO_4:
526  if (Creature* saurfang = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _factionNPC))
527  saurfang->AI()->Talk(SAY_SAURFANG_INTRO_4);
528  break;
529  case EVENT_MURADIN_RUN:
530  case EVENT_SAURFANG_RUN:
531  if (Creature* factionNPC = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _factionNPC))
532  {
533  factionNPC->GetMotionMaster()->MovePath(factionNPC->GetSpawnId() * 10, false);
534  factionNPC->DespawnOrUnsummon(46500);
535  std::list<Creature*> followers;
536  factionNPC->GetCreaturesWithEntryInRange(followers, 30, _instance->GetData(DATA_TEAMID_IN_INSTANCE) == TEAM_HORDE ? NPC_KOR_KRON_GENERAL : NPC_ALLIANCE_COMMANDER);
537  for (Creature* follower : followers)
538  {
539  follower->DespawnOrUnsummon(46500);
540  }
541  }
542  me->setActive(false);
543  _damnedKills = 3;
544  break;
545  case EVENT_MURADIN_INTRO_1:
546  if (Creature* muradin = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, _factionNPC))
547  muradin->AI()->Talk(SAY_MURADIN_INTRO_1);
